PHARAOH

Bomb/Defuse Map for Counter-Strike: Source

CS:GO original map creator: Motanum
CS:S map port creator: Niko
Navigation Mesh editor: Meurglis3

High-quality port for CS:S of same-named midsize map from CS:GO by Motanum / Eugenio Roman. Map set on a fictional Egyptian theme park section. This port contains some constructive and visual changes in comparison with the original, which was made for bigger detailing and improvement of the gameplay smoothness.

Story:
   A few weeks from the grand opening of Pharaoh's Curse, the new roller coaster at Roaring Peaks has been picked as the target of the Phoenix Connection.

P.S. ~ My name is an erased hieroglyph, my clothes are patched by the wind... :-)

A Bomb/Defuse map with many secrets!

Hello all!
Here i come with a new map that i've finished last week but didnt uploaded here.
So, i think you may know the original map cs_assaultgoban created by Barking Dog Studios and also the creator for  Backalley and i hated this map because of its poor texture design.

So for that i decided to create a modern remake but with some major updates like:
- i have eliminated the hostages
- the CT spawn is now inverted with T spawn. The terrorists have to make assault to plant the bomb in bombsite A or B.
- modern texture

So, credits go to:
- Original creator: Barking Dog Studios
- Texture used: saspatoon

If you play on this map and you enjoy it, please rate and comment.

DE_PETRO
=========
Author: Derek Braun
Date: 03/10/2008
Build  Time: 3 weeks
Players: 24

Description:
==========
Terrorists have seized a chemical processing facility in the heart of a industrial complex. They are threatening to destroy the complex and thus putting the entire region in danger of chemical radiation and a subsequent meltdown.  This map utilizes many vantage points that players can use to their advantage, no matter what side, to gain an edge. Good luck!
Don't spectate outside the map or an error will occur!

de_peacemaker - Bomb/Defuse
Map made by: Xanthi (xanthi_mapdesign@hotmail.com)
textures Valve
Models : Valve

background :
After the big disaster in de_industrial_compound the goverment said to the media.
They stopped the production of uranium and other nuclear material.
But afcourse it was one big lie.
Some weeks ago a satelite spotted a island with higly nuclear activity.
The Allies where so mad about this that they leaked the information to a terrorist leader.
You know terrorists, they like to blow up stuff, specially a island with nuclear material.


Counter-Terrorists: You've received
a tip about activities at the Island
That's the reason why you guys are hidden
at the Island, to stop the terrorists.
Defend it at all cost.


Terrorists:
Blow up the whole island to whipe it out forever
option 1: place a bomb at the trainstation with tank wagons
option 2: place a bomb at in the nuclear warehouse
It doesnt matter what target you choose the buildings are connected with a pipeline that transporting
nuclear toxic.
So there is always one big boom.

Other Notes: There are 2 possible ways
to cause a chemical disaster.
Awsome fun map hope gets good wrap :)

Author: Titan1x77

Name: de_pawtucket_v2

Release notes: .nav and radar overviews are packed into the BSP

Type: Bomb/Diffuse; 64 spawns, 12v12 is ideal for this map.

Description: Small intense map with quick routes to sites, with an larger outer area to take a long way around to Bombsite B (also branches off to A a few times). Bombsite A is more open but has a lower area underground to help cover it, bomb can be planted on roof aswell. Access to high vantage points everywhere and a few small areas with vent access too! 

Build notes: about 80 hours, first time using Hammer (so it's my first complete map), learned a lot while making this level, and enjoyed doing so. Concentrated on gameplay/balance more then looks, wanted to keep framerate as high as possible for an large outdoor area map.

Thanks to chizbone for the .nav!

Enjoy!

Release notes: This version is final, HDR and a better bot .nav will be used for v2 (version 2) with any bug fixes. Old .nav and radar overviews are packed into the BSP, New .nav by Chizbone is in the .zip (just place into /maps folder)

Type: Bomb/Diffuse; 64 spawns, 12v12 is ideal for this map.

Description: Small intense map with quick routes to sites, with an larger outer area to take a long way around to Bombsite B (also branches off to A a few times). Bombsite A is more open but has a lower area underground to help cover it, bomb can be planted on roof aswell. Access to high vantage points everywhere and a few small areas with vent access too! 

Build notes: about 80 hours, first time using Hammer (so it's my first complete map), learned a lot while making this level, and enjoyed doing so. Concentrated on gameplay/balance more then looks, wanted to keep framerate as high as possible for an large outdoor area map.

Enjoy!

INFO:
F a m i l y P a s t a - Defusion
by -Stratesiz- 

Storyline:

The FBI has been informed of a possible strike against the mafia family leader in New Jersey by an anonymous call to a local police station. Once the police had reason to believe the threat was real they evacuated Bernardigio Nuccio's family from his residence which was located above his Italian restaurant. The police know that the restaurant itself has served as a meeting place for Nuccio's organisation, consequently making it the perfect location for a revenge performed by another mafia family.


Counter-Terrorists:
Your mission is to stop this unnecesary strike of terror at all cost. You have been informed of a possible bomb threat which is to be prevented by any means neccesary. Secure the the entire building. Do not let this operation turn into a big bowl of bloody pasta!

Terrorists:
Your primary objective will be to eliminate Bernardigio Nuccio and his family. The secondary goal is to "clean" out all evidence of your presence by planting a bomb in one of the two strategical bomb spots. These two locations will be the most efficient way to cause destruction to this filthy mafia family that betrayed us.
"

Have FUN !

Made by RAD

*********************************

 The original de_paris map received very favourable reviews, and became quite popular, particularly in France.  There were some issues with framerate in certain parts of the map, and hence this highly optimized version was developed.   The lighting in the metro has also been redone, as well as some other  minor changes in certain places.  We hope you enjoy this new, high FPS version of de_paris_opt!!    

*********************************

-------
PARIS
-------
Bomb defusion map.
-----------------
Map Created by ATF_RealSeal
mapping_predator@hotmail.com
-----------------
Optimized by Swift
-----------------
5th June 2008
-----------------

Version:  de_paris_opt (OPTIMIZED)
--------

STORY:
--------
Terrorists have occupied an area of Paris, and want to cause as much destruction as possible. Their primary target is the famous cafe "Les Deux Magots", and their backup plan is to blow up the Abbesses Metro station.

Inspired by the Euopean-feel of cs_italy, and also the fantastic gameplay of de_dust2. The dimensions are almost exactly the same as those of de_dust2, and the layout shares some similar elements. 

FEATURES:
-----------
- Intelligent nav file 
- Radar overview map
- Fully immersive ambience
- Custom models, textures, soundscape, 3D skybox

CREDITS:
----------
Map by ATF_RealSeal (aka S.E.A.L. #555, aka Predulus, aka A.o.F).  Optimization by Swift.

Thanks to Ralph Van Hoorn for optimizing help, Ltk and members of clans S013 and REAL for testing, Dave Johnston (Author of Dust and Dust2) for feedback. CFoust for helping me with a sound problem. My wife for putting up with me mapping all the time.

FUN: 
-------
- Try killing the Crows. They're hard to hit.
- You can also press the "USE" key on the i-Pod.
- See if you can find the secret sounds and passageways
- Items of special interest may be the Arc de Triomphe and the Eiffel Tower.
